::Aerotaur::
       He raises himself up very elegantly.  "I am the noble ... uh ... I 
don't know my own name.  That can't be good."  He sighs and his shoulders 
sag.  He looks over his body.  "Well, ... I look like a centaur, only i have 
wings.  All right call me Aerotaur."  He shrugs.  "I guess it's as good as my 
real name, whatever that is."
